# YouTube OAuth (Orbix Network – Connect YouTube / auto-publish)
# Get credentials: Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application).
# Add authorized redirect URI: https://YOUR-BACKEND-DOMAIN/api/v2/orbix-network/youtube/callback
# Copy these into your .env (and into Railway Environment if deployed):

YOUTUBE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
YOUTUBE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here
YOUTUBE_REDIRECT_URI=https://your-backend-domain.com/api/v2/orbix-network/youtube/callback
